Classifier: Operating System :: MacOS
Requires-Python: >=3.8
Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
License-File: LICENSE

You can use this to help synthesise narration of audio books if live readers are not available.  As the synthesised audio is likely to have pronunciation glitches, some custom programming specific to your book will almost certainly be required.

